âœ¨ Black Formatter

Publisher: Microsoft
Extension ID: ms-python.black-formatter

Black is an opinionated Python code formatter.

---

Why it is important

-Automatically formats your code
-Ensures consistent style across projects
-Main features
-One-click formatting
-Follows PEP 8 standards
-Eliminates style debates

âœ… Used in professional and enterprise projects.

