ğŸ“ autoDocstring

Publisher: Nils Werner
Extension ID: njpwerner.autodocstring

autoDocstring automatically generates Python docstrings.

---

Why it is important

-Encourages documentation
-Saves time writing docstrings
-Improves code readability
-Main features
-One-command docstring generation
-Supports multiple docstring styles (Google, NumPy)
-Improves maintainability

âœ… Highly recommended for clean, professional Python code.

